definitions.definition: An annual publication ; a book , periodical , journal , report , comic book , yearbook , etc., which is published serially once a year, which may or may not be in addition to regular weekly or monthly publication.
examples: I read the magazine, but I usually don't purchase the annuals .

definitions.definition: An annual plant ; a plant with a life span of just one growing season; a plant which naturally germinates , flowers and dies in one year. Compare biennial , perennial .
examples: I can't wait to plant my annuals in the spring.

definitions.definition: A medical checkup taking place once a year.
A pantomime taking place once a year.
